  "remarks": "TAi.101 Title: Maulavi. Designation: Governor of Laghman Province under the Taliban regime. Taliban commander for Ghazni Province as at 2008. Belongs to Andar tribe. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 23 Jul. 2010.; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 23 February 2001 (amended on 21 Sep 2007, 29 Nov. 2011)",
